               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="82r" facs="007">Fols 1r–82r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas">Sayfa Śǝllāse</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ብክሙ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አነ፡ ኃጥእ፡ በከመ፡ አተውክሙ፡ ቤተ፡ አብርሃም፡ ከማሁ፡ አእትዉኒ፡ ውስተ፡ መንበርክሙ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Arranged for days of the week</note>
