                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                    <locus target="#95v #96r" facs="102">Fols. 95v, 96r</locus>
                    “It is finished Sane 10, 1961 EC. The scribe is Mäkwonǝn Mäqwuriya. His baptismal name is Täklä Ṣadǝq. His native land is Mänz, the exact place is Giyorgis.”
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ ሰኔ፡ ፲፩፡ ቀን፡ ፲፱፻፷፩ዓ፡ ምሕረት፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ መኰንን፡ መኵሪያ፡ ወስመ፡ ጥምቀቱ፡ ተክለ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ብሔረ፡ ሙላዱ፡ መንዝ፡ ክፍለ፡ ሀገሩ፡ ዋካ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign>
                  </colophon>
